<Author>A TripAdvisor Member
<Content>in the middle of Mitte ! We stayed here for 3 nights and are very enthusiastic about it. It's right in the middle of Berlin Mitte: 600 metres from the Reichstag and about 10 minutes from Unter den Linden. Bahnhof Friedrichsstrasse is just around the corner! And yet the Albrechsstrasse is very peaceful and calm with cosy little restaurants and caf茅s (Schiffbaudamm is in the neighbourhood, great to have a drink there on a terrace esp. late at night).Our room was big, sober and clean, just as we like it. We were very pleased with it!The breakfast (buffet) was excellent and the staff friendly. A minor detail : the breakfast-room was a bit too small.The ratings are okay. We loved Berlin (and this hotel) so much that we want to go back next year. I hope we will have a room in the Allegra Hotel again. 
