<Content>Great location, good value I loved staying at the Hotel Allegra! The location was fantastic, right near the Friedrichstrasse station, which is smack in the middle of everything. In walking distance to Unter den Linden and a lot of the historic sites. Very good breakfast, rooms were clean and comfortable though rather small, especially the bathroom, which reminded me of a space capsule. Across the street is its sister hotel, which has a restaurant and is more upscale (and more expensive). 
